<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 01:54:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>纽约证券交易所所有者和 OKX 将推出与石油挂钩的永续期货</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-22/nyse-owner-and-okx-seek-to-launch-perpetual-futures-tied-to-oil</link><description>纽约证券交易所的所有者洲际交易所公司正在与加密货币交易所运营商 OKX 合作推出永不过期的石油期货合约。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihSqoTF5GRwM/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-22/nyse-owner-and-okx-seek-to-launch-perpetual-futures-tied-to-oil</guid></item><item><title>韩国调查 Polymarket 是否存在潜在赌博违规行为</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-22/south-korea-probes-polymarket-for-potential-gambling-violations</link><description>韩国媒体监管机构正在审查 Polymarket 的平台是否包含非法赌博内容，这是全球最大预测市场之一监管压力不断加大的最新迹象。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igAQ3L1wtvRk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 03:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-22/south-korea-probes-polymarket-for-potential-gambling-violations</guid></item><item><title>快速行动和打破常规正在为 Tokenizer 带来回报</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-21/moving-fast-and-breaking-things-is-paying-off-for-crypto-tokenizers</link><description>市场正在对有利于创新的规则的未来进行定价。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQ6TrkMA9IPU/v8/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-21/moving-fast-and-breaking-things-is-paying-off-for-crypto-tokenizers</guid></item><item><title>当价格开始回升时，比特币投资者抛售最多</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-21/for-bitcoin-etf-holders-a-market-recovery-is-a-reason-to-sell</link><description>比特币 ETF 的糟糕流出暴露了加密货币市场结构中一种令人不安的动态：本应吸引买家回归的价格水平也引发了一些最严重的抛售。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igwvQQkAX9gU/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 15:46:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-21/for-bitcoin-etf-holders-a-market-recovery-is-a-reason-to-sell</guid></item><item><title>Blockchain.com 秘密提交美国公开发行文件</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-21/blockchain-com-files-confidentially-for-initial-public-offering</link><description>Blockchain.com Group Holdings Inc. 是最古老的加密服务公司之一，已向美国证券交易委员会秘密提交首次公开募股申请，加入了在该行业最动荡时期之一寻求上市的大量数字资产公司的行列。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUGdwd2OqRWo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-21/blockchain-com-files-confidentially-for-initial-public-offering</guid></item></channel></rss>